    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows clear signs of age, including some cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor exterior scuffs. It has been used regularly, and while it starts and runs reliably, a new owner should expect to perform some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in good working order.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
